00:01:54,340 --> 00:01:58,060
=Miss Crow With Mr. Lizard=

20
00:01:58,980 --> 00:02:02,060
=Episode 32=

21
00:02:23,200 --> 00:02:23,720
Here.

22
00:02:28,800 --> 00:02:30,440
Yan Yan, something happened to Gu Chuan!

23
00:02:56,920 --> 00:02:57,520
You're awake.

24
00:03:11,320 --> 00:03:12,800
Why did you bring her here?

25
00:03:14,480 --> 00:03:15,520
I've told her everything.

26
00:03:16,920 --> 00:03:18,040
You swore

27
00:03:18,200 --> 00:03:19,160
you wouldn't tell anyone.

28
00:03:19,280 --> 00:03:19,800
Yes.

29
00:03:19,960 --> 00:03:20,760
I did say

30
00:03:20,920 --> 00:03:21,720
that if I were to tell anyone,

31
00:03:21,840 --> 00:03:23,000
I would be struck by lightning.

32
00:03:23,520 --> 00:03:24,760
But Yan Yan isn't anyone.

33
00:03:25,120 --> 00:03:26,000
She's my wife.

34
00:03:26,320 --> 00:03:26,800
Right?

35
00:03:27,760 --> 00:03:28,640
Don't worry.

36
00:03:28,800 --> 00:03:30,320
I won't tell anyone.

37
00:03:30,840 --> 00:03:31,600
Also,

38
00:03:32,840 --> 00:03:34,120
I wanted to visit you as well.

39
00:03:40,800 --> 00:03:42,040
Did you get me here?

40
00:03:42,400 --> 00:03:44,520
Yes, there is a low battery alarm.

41
00:03:44,920 --> 00:03:46,560
Did you forget to charge again?

42
00:03:46,880 --> 00:03:47,920
If you keep doing this,

43
00:03:48,040 --> 00:03:49,600
that'll be suicide.

44
00:03:51,400 --> 00:03:53,280
It was my negligence.

45
00:03:54,840 --> 00:03:55,600
Earlier,

46
00:03:56,720 --> 00:03:57,360
I thought

47
00:03:57,440 --> 00:03:58,560
my time was up

48
00:03:59,440 --> 00:04:00,440
and that I was going to die.

49
00:04:02,800 --> 00:04:04,000
Thank you

50
00:04:04,720 --> 00:04:07,120
for making it here timely and saving me.

51
00:04:08,680 --> 00:04:09,560
Knock it off.

52
00:04:14,360 --> 00:04:15,560
It's good to have you.

53
00:04:27,520 --> 00:04:28,680
Gu Chuan, I'm sorry.

54
00:04:29,720 --> 00:04:30,960
I misunderstood you.

55
00:04:32,120 --> 00:04:33,520
I kept telling Xiao Ning

56
00:04:33,680 --> 00:04:34,320
that you were a jerk

57
00:04:34,360 --> 00:04:35,640
to treat her that way.

58
00:04:36,680 --> 00:04:38,480
But after hearing your condition from
Xu Cheng Ran,

59
00:04:40,040 --> 00:04:41,120
what you did for Xiao Ning

60
00:04:41,240 --> 00:04:42,720
was really noble.

61
00:04:44,520 --> 00:04:45,360
In this world,

62
00:04:45,480 --> 00:04:46,880
you're the man who loves Xiao Ning the most.

63
00:04:49,680 --> 00:04:50,680
I apologize to you.

64
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:53,880
Thank you

65
00:04:54,680 --> 00:04:55,840
for using your own way

66
00:04:56,560 --> 00:04:57,840
to love Xiao Ning.

67
00:05:06,400 --> 00:05:08,040
Here's your wedding gift.

68
00:05:08,480 --> 00:05:09,240
What is it?

69
00:05:09,800 --> 00:05:10,800
It's a painting.

70
00:05:11,360 --> 00:05:12,440
I painted it a long time ago.

71
00:05:12,600 --> 00:05:13,920
But I didn't have the chance to give it to you.

72
00:05:16,400 --> 00:05:17,520
Thank you, Xiao Ning.

73
00:05:19,360 --> 00:05:19,960
Wen Wen.

74
00:05:20,480 --> 00:05:21,960
How long will you be there this time?

75
00:05:22,640 --> 00:05:25,080
I think I'll be there for quite some time.

76
00:05:25,200 --> 00:05:25,880
Otherwise,

77
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:27,240
I wouldn't have asked you out

78
00:05:27,360 --> 00:05:28,360
to say goodbye to you.

79
00:05:29,760 --> 00:05:31,840
After we're married,

80
00:05:31,960 --> 00:05:33,480
we don't intend to settle down in one place.

81
00:05:33,600 --> 00:05:35,200
So we plan to travel first

82
00:05:35,280 --> 00:05:36,680
and think about where to live later on.

83
00:05:37,200 --> 00:05:39,360
I'm so envious of you. Such a perfect couple.

84
00:05:39,560 --> 00:05:41,000
What's there to envy?

85
00:05:41,160 --> 00:05:41,840
There are different

86
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:43,840
types of happiness in life.

87
00:05:44,120 --> 00:05:45,120
Speaking of which,

88
00:05:45,280 --> 00:05:47,160
you don't look so great.

89
00:05:47,720 --> 00:05:48,880
Are you too exhausted?

90
00:05:49,360 --> 00:05:50,080
Do I?

91
00:05:51,360 --> 00:05:52,800
There are things

92
00:05:52,920 --> 00:05:53,800
that haven't been taken care of.

93
00:05:57,480 --> 00:05:59,360
How are you and Gu Chuan?

94
00:06:01,840 --> 00:06:04,400
Mr. Xu said he went on a vacation.

95
00:06:05,000 --> 00:06:06,760
I haven't seen him for quite some time.

96
00:06:08,920 --> 00:06:10,280
This is my own business.

97
00:06:10,440 --> 00:06:11,560
You can just leave me alone.

98
00:06:12,920 --> 00:06:13,680
I know.

99
00:06:14,560 --> 00:06:15,880
I'm being meddlesome.

100
00:06:17,320 --> 00:06:19,440
I just hope you and Jiang Xiao Ning

101
00:06:19,600 --> 00:06:20,720
can be happy.

102
00:06:21,680 --> 00:06:23,240
If you just let her pass you by like this,

103
00:06:24,120 --> 00:06:25,680
I will feel sad for you.

104
00:06:26,480 --> 00:06:28,080
I'm the one who feels the saddest.

105
00:06:34,000 --> 00:06:34,880
Do you know

106
00:06:35,040 --> 00:06:36,640
about his mechanical heart?

107
00:06:38,240 --> 00:06:39,320
He told me.

108
00:06:39,880 --> 00:06:43,160
And he saved me in the car accident

109
00:06:43,640 --> 00:06:44,720
ten years ago.

110
00:06:52,920 --> 00:06:53,760
I didn't know you two

111
00:06:53,920 --> 00:06:55,680
had such a story.

112
00:06:59,120 --> 00:06:59,800
Xiao Ning.

113
00:07:01,080 --> 00:07:01,720
I can't comment

114
00:07:01,880 --> 00:07:03,400
on your relationship.

115
00:07:03,840 --> 00:07:04,760
But I think

116
00:07:04,920 --> 00:07:06,440
Gu Chuan is the kind of person

117
00:07:06,560 --> 00:07:07,880
who keeps

118
00:07:08,000 --> 00:07:09,120
everything to himself.

119
00:07:10,080 --> 00:07:10,920
So if you don't want

120
00:07:11,040 --> 00:07:12,320
to give up on him just yet,

121
00:07:12,960 --> 00:07:13,640
I think

122
00:07:13,800 --> 00:07:14,720
