125
00:07:19,160 --> 00:07:20,560
Feel with your heart.

126
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:29,320
Whatever your decision is,

127
00:07:29,480 --> 00:07:30,280
I'll have your back.

128
00:07:31,960 --> 00:07:32,640
All the best.

129
00:07:37,880 --> 00:07:38,440
See you.

