190
00:12:37,200 --> 00:12:37,680
That's right.

191
00:12:38,400 --> 00:12:39,520
Didn't he sign

192
00:12:39,600 --> 00:12:40,560
the consent form?

193
00:12:41,040 --> 00:12:41,840
Didn't he tell you?

194
00:12:42,160 --> 00:12:43,080
He did sign the form.

195
00:12:43,400 --> 00:12:44,600
But he couldn't bear to do it.

196
00:12:44,760 --> 00:12:45,600
After much deliberation,

197
00:12:46,040 --> 00:12:47,320
he changed his mind.

198
00:12:50,000 --> 00:12:50,760
Here is the money.

199
00:13:52,800 --> 00:13:53,840
