200
00:13:53,920 --> 00:13:54,560
Thank you.

201
00:13:55,000 --> 00:13:55,440
All right.

202
00:14:03,280 --> 00:14:05,080
(Jiang Xiao Ning)
Sir, the cement's here.

203
00:14:05,080 --> 00:14:05,560
(Jiang Xiao Ning)
Okay.

204
00:14:05,560 --> 00:14:06,680
(Jiang Xiao Ning)
Speed up.

205
00:14:06,680 --> 00:14:07,240
(Jiang Xiao Ning)
Thank you.

206
00:14:21,280 --> 00:14:22,840
(Xiao Ning, what's the matter?)

207
00:14:23,920 --> 00:14:24,960
Do you remember

208
00:14:24,960 --> 00:14:26,200
what I told you about Ice Cream?

209
00:14:27,280 --> 00:14:28,400
I thought Gu Chuan

210
00:14:28,480 --> 00:14:29,720
signed the consent form for euthanasia.

211
00:14:29,880 --> 00:14:31,200
But today the pet hospital called

212
00:14:31,320 --> 00:14:32,840
and told me to get the refund.

213
00:14:33,240 --> 00:14:35,200
The vet told me that Gu Chuan changed his mind

214
00:14:35,680 --> 00:14:37,000
about the euthanasia injection

215
00:14:37,160 --> 00:14:38,640
and took Ice Cream back.

216
00:14:39,520 --> 00:14:40,200
I wanted to ask him

217
00:14:40,360 --> 00:14:41,480
what actually happened.

218
00:14:41,640 --> 00:14:42,400
But I called him twice

219
00:14:42,440 --> 00:14:44,280
and there was no answer.

220
00:14:45,280 --> 00:14:46,960
Could you ask Mr. Xu for me

221
00:14:47,120 --> 00:14:47,800
if he knew

222
00:14:47,920 --> 00:14:49,000
where Gu Chuan had gone to?

223
00:14:50,480 --> 00:14:51,800
I didn't hear him talk about it.

224
00:14:54,480 --> 00:14:55,360
Sister Yan Yan.

225
00:14:56,040 --> 00:14:57,880
I'm so confused now.

226
00:14:58,320 --> 00:14:59,360
I can't help thinking

227
00:14:59,480 --> 00:15:00,640
like things aren't that simple.

228
00:15:01,280 --> 00:15:03,000
Could you ask Mr. Xu for me

229
00:15:03,320 --> 00:15:04,400
if he knew

230
00:15:04,520 --> 00:15:05,520
where Gu Chuan had gone to?

231
00:15:10,960 --> 00:15:12,160
Do you really want to know?

232
00:15:12,680 --> 00:15:13,520
Of course.

233
00:15:14,440 --> 00:15:14,920
Sister Yan Yan.

234
00:15:15,040 --> 00:15:16,040
Do you know something?

235
00:15:16,200 --> 00:15:17,720
Tell me, please.

236
00:15:21,080 --> 00:15:23,200
Gu Chuan took Ice Cream back

237
00:15:23,960 --> 00:15:25,080
and accompanied Ice Cream

238
00:15:25,240 --> 00:15:26,280
during its final hours.

239
00:15:26,880 --> 00:15:28,080
He didn't tell you

240
00:15:28,400 --> 00:15:29,480
because he was afraid

241
00:15:29,640 --> 00:15:30,720
the pain would be too much to you.

242
00:15:31,280 --> 00:15:34,000
(Xiao Ning, Gu Chuan was trying to protect you.)

243
00:15:34,520 --> 00:15:35,480
What do you mean?

244
00:15:35,800 --> 00:15:37,480
Did he tell you these

245
00:15:37,600 --> 00:15:39,080
or it was just a wild guess?

246
00:15:39,840 --> 00:15:41,200
Xiao Ning, stop asking questions.

247
00:15:41,360 --> 00:15:42,600
Did it cross your mind

248
00:15:42,720 --> 00:15:44,160
Gu Chuan's current situation

249
00:15:44,640 --> 00:15:45,640
is similar

250
00:15:45,640 --> 00:15:46,600
to Ice Cream's?

251
00:15:48,280 --> 00:15:49,680
What are you talking about?

252
00:15:50,080 --> 00:15:51,560
What is similar?

253
00:15:52,120 --> 00:15:54,200
Sister Yan Yan, just tell me, please.

254
00:15:54,680 --> 00:15:56,080
(Xiao Ning, ask no more.)

255
00:15:56,400 --> 00:15:58,280
Think about your wish.

256
00:15:58,600 --> 00:15:59,520
Think with your heart.

257
00:15:59,960 --> 00:16:01,680
You'll know where he is.

258
00:16:44,600 --> 00:16:46,720
(Sorry, the number you have dialed)

259
00:16:46,880 --> 00:16:48,080
(cannot be reached temporarily.)

260
00:17:39,160 --> 00:17:39,839
Gu Chuan.

261
00:17:59,960 --> 00:18:01,200
You shouldn't be here.

262
00:18:05,120 --> 00:18:06,480
So you hiding here and rebuilding my family house

263
00:18:06,560 --> 00:18:07,400
