264
00:18:09,720 --> 00:18:10,840
I just want to help you

265
00:18:11,080 --> 00:18:12,880
rebuild your family home.

266
00:18:13,240 --> 00:18:14,440
Who are you to help me?

267
00:18:15,440 --> 00:18:16,480
You don't even want me.

268
00:18:16,560 --> 00:18:17,160
What's the point

269
00:18:17,200 --> 00:18:18,320
of you fulfilling my dream?

270
00:18:23,680 --> 00:18:25,080
I'm such a fool.

271
00:18:25,960 --> 00:18:27,240
I was with you all the time.

272
00:18:27,720 --> 00:18:28,680
I should have known

273
00:18:28,800 --> 00:18:30,000
you weren't feeling well.

274
00:18:30,480 --> 00:18:31,520
I should have known

275
00:18:31,680 --> 00:18:32,920
that you were lying to me.

276
00:18:35,840 --> 00:18:37,120
Regardless,

277
00:18:38,080 --> 00:18:39,560
we can't be together anymore.

278
00:18:40,480 --> 00:18:41,280
Why?

279
00:18:45,080 --> 00:18:45,760
I don't want

280
00:18:45,880 --> 00:18:47,080
to tie you down with me.

281
00:18:48,160 --> 00:18:49,800
You can have a better future.

282
00:18:50,960 --> 00:18:52,560
I don't want you to regret it in the future.

283
00:18:53,524 --> 00:18:54,044
That's right.

284
00:18:54,960 --> 00:18:55,640
Gu Chuan.

